drm: Turn DRM_MODE_SUBCONNECTOR_xx definitions into an enum

List of values like the DRM_MODE_SUBCONNECTOR_xx ones are better
represented with enums.

Turn the DRM_MODE_SUBCONNECTOR_xx macros into an enum.

